                        "@id": "/lore_entry_element_types/01GR6AE2ZSVVYP6SDJXN8Q5DVF",
                        "@type": "LoreEntryElementType",
                        "id": "01GR6AE2ZSVVYP6SDJXN8Q5DVF",
                        "reference": "STORY",
                        "subject": "Story"
                    },
                    "text": "\"He departs into the void and the chaos within;\r\nEntering the Tumult, he embraces its essence;\r\nHe delights in it, trusting it with every sense;\r\nHe absorbs the energy, into soul and onto skin;\r\n\r\nIn that instant, that moment, the transformation takes place;\r\nThe eager initiate now understands that his nature;\r\nFar from being fixed and unique, is just a signature;\r\nMany-faced and ever-changing, it constantly regenerates;\r\n\r\nHe accepts the burden of his intense transformation;\r\nThe sign of his Faction and the source of its might;\r\nFor all, he wants only to bring joy and to excite;\r\nFrom the magic he creates, art is its expression;\r\n\r\nReturning from this journey and into a new dimension;\r\nHe celebrates Ignescence, and the change it brings;\r\nAnd inspired by the power of all these feelings;\r\nFrom the Tumult reshaped, he becomes its champion.\"\r"
                },
